    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "so if the transit isn't good enough yet, then isn't it pretty much just a way to penalize people for working? like, if you're someone who has to drive because the subway is unreliable or doesn't go where you need, isn't this just an unfair way to squeeze more money out of people who don't have other options?",
